desc_long								关于这款游戏							Note : This VR Experience requires an HTC VIVE /Oculus Rift & the latest STEAM VR / Oculus runtime VISIT ONE OF THE GREATEST NATURAL WONDERS OF THE WORLD A VR-FIRST Experience designed for maximum immersion Explore the beauty and splendor of the Grand Canyon via kayak (Oculus) or stand-up paddle-board (Vive) Vivid, living world populated with procedural generation of animal life driven by artificial intelligence Enjoy a fully dynamic day & night cycle Help us on our quest to create the world's first highly immersive living virtual Grand Canyon!MECHANICS Use the motion controllers to paddle the Colorado River at various speeds Discover new area's and interact with new animals Watch the sun go down and explore the Canyon under a starry sky Use a flashlight when exploring the Canyon at night Many more mechanics in the works!EARLY ACCESS ADVANTAGE Get access to this living VR world right now Regular updates with new features and bug fixes Influence future development and features						
